{"tid":184253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒法去掃墓怎辦？ 淘寶「代掃墓人」應運而生","createTime":"2017-04-02T16:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T05:48:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0bd4292513134f5abe3b9b092f6ce1bcc4959e","tid":184253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpUXN2No.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpUXN2No.jpg&h=666528b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017-04-02  22:26<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕許多人會在清明時節去掃墓，但現代人生活繁忙，於是「代掃墓人」這項工作便應運而生，中國有名男子喬羅男（化名）在淘寶上專職「代掃墓人」已經2年，他並遵守著「代掃墓人」的2大規矩：一不下跪、二不假哭，喬羅男認為這不只是生意，更是一種成人之美。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，今年27歲的喬羅男表示，一場15分鐘的祭祀，他必須找墓地、採購、確認流程等，常提前3天就開始準備，一天更可能有多場訂單，沒有幫手，全都自己來。<br />\n他回憶起第一次掃墓時，山裡的老墳沒有號碼，連委託人都說不太清楚墓地位置，跑了好幾趟他才找到，到了開始祭祀當天，他開直播錄影，卻一句話也說不出來，「站在陌生人的墓碑前還是有點發懵的，心理上有所忌憚，不知如何將委託給我的話，說給另一個世界的人聽」。<br />\n喬羅男熟悉後，開始客制化不同服務，依照不同服務也有不同收費，像是一次祭祀大概需要15分鐘，最高的一次收費800元人民幣。而清明時是這些「代掃墓人」最忙的時候，另一名「代掃墓人」小珂說，他已經好幾年沒有在清明回家了。<br />\n除了喬羅男和小珂，在淘寶上還有許多「代掃墓人」，他們都遵守著「代掃墓人」的2大規矩：一不下跪、二不假哭，因為「有些情緒應該是發自內心的，不能讓陌生人表達，也不應該用錢買到。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2024475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2024475&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c64d1cba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2024475&h=228b7f3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2024475</a>"},{"pid":"b5ce71f2a25c6694f2112320f3f0d26f77453fb4","tid":184253,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"淘寶有冇代返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590a9e4c8d86a68a7528f1d186f0e74d80735de7","tid":184253,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T22:40:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41ef278668f5eacc43a79b9069c7b610efb10d87","tid":184253,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"電子拜山算la~"},{"pid":"22c268fff86ab6ab8ccb88c7adc03d2c40a77968","tid":184253,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:36:20.000Z","msg":"代掃墓其實唔係咩新鮮事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15488103a22f1756e8eb0ba17cb7a87212e1a58","tid":184253,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淘寶有冇代返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想淘個返嚟</blockquote><br />\n唔洗淘寶咁煩<br />\n<br />\n同你老細講咪得"},{"pid":"e5f834e8a9ac973044679827a9ddb391b4b4eaf0","tid":184253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ec06335a72a1bf81cd327ee498602b2243f56","tid":184253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}